reviewText: There are 10 episodes for $15.  I bought this first, then started buying the complete season package.  Very good tv show from the 60's with lots of up and coming actors.  Can't go wrong if you just want a sample from season 1.
As good as I remembered as a kid
Great, but don't spend your money on just the first ten episodes, buy the whole series!  A flat-out classic. Not ever to be equaled again.
